data.description: Highly sought after well maintained four bedroom, two bath home in South Anchorage. Three bedrooms upstairs. Main bedroom downstairs with walk-in closet. Large covered back deck patio. Fenced backyard with storage shed. New hot water heater and furnace in 2021. New roof in 2015. Remodel included flooring, appliances, and paint! Newer stainless steel appliances. Will go fast!! Don't miss out!
